{"tid":1192788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司法機構稱有法官聯署反對修訂《逃犯條例》","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T15:09:36.000Z","uid":117622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7fa327d3442d00b5829f2b63543d63dc47f758","tid":1192788,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"港大校友關注組在社交網站及報章刊登早前收集到超過3000個簽名，反對政府修訂《逃犯條例》。聯署名單中其中一個簽名為「李瀚良」，畢業年份是1986年，與現任高等法院原訟法庭法官李瀚良同名，畢業年份亦相同。<br />\n<br />\n本台向司法機構查詢，李瀚良法官有否參與聯署，司法機構回覆時證實，有法官參與是次聯署，並指終審法院首席法官馬道立曾與該法官討論，知悉對方以個人名義參與聯署，馬道立勸告對方將來應避免同類事情發生，司法機構指，該法官表示同意馬道立的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461616-20190608.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461616-20190608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSSJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=c28f2a0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461616-20190608.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cd2a650e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461616-20190608.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"42ff2b8463c0db8416f559eae8d2dfb2792c0a64","tid":1192788,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;If you want peace, prepare for war.&rdquo;<br />\nFrom John Wick 3: Parabellum"}]}